{"tid":2025314,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"抗日戰爭關支共咩事?","createTime":"2020-05-20T07:08:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-20T08:14:59.000Z","uid":19552,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0225e18cccace791395e63ce8ebf8e3f150e395b","tid":2025314,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T07:08:27.000Z","msg":"七二一方針，又稱七分發展、二分應付、一分抗日<br />\n<br />\n抗日期間支那軍打民國國軍仲大力過日本皇軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cab28ae4539415bb18e59f6777cc131bc7ad11e4","tid":2025314,"uid":74622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T07:09:31.000Z","msg":"國共內戰打打下之後日本侵華<br />\n都係國民黨打遊擊<br />\n共產黨匿埋咗<br />\n匿到珍珠港事件<br />\n美國投放兩粒原子彈去廣島同埋長崎<br />\n日本仔先投降 (如果冇投降 你同我都講緊日文)<br />\n跟住共產黨先伸個頭出嚟攬晒啲功勞<br />\n表面上緊係冇輸過<br />\n<br />\n史實"},{"pid":"ead1a8187c9143f1d097fff27061518706cfcf92","tid":2025314,"uid":237562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T07:10:30.000Z","msg":"共諜有份暗中策劃蘆溝橋事變屈日本仔"},{"pid":"68441aa2e70153c5f3d4c3b0561c46be781a7259","tid":2025314,"uid":45518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T07:10:56.000Z","msg":"抗日戰爭令支共掘起殘害人間呀，咁都冇關係？"},{"pid":"a5476765137204c2cc286c656573b4d1bd3951eb","tid":2025314,"uid":17606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T07:30:43.000Z","msg":"有外憂就冇內患<br />\n反正假想敵就係萬惡之源"},{"pid":"9964cd9686641d0fe279f124f2a80e1380ddb101","tid":2025314,"uid":209644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"68441aa2e70153c5f3d4c3b0561c46be781a7259","tid":2025314,"uid":45518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T07:10:56.000Z","msg":"抗日戰爭令支共掘起殘害人間呀，咁都冇關係？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T08:14:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"